solution: ```class Solution {
    public String[] sortPeople(String[] names, int[] heights) {
        int n = names.length;
        int[][] idx = new int[n][2];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            idx[i][0] = i;
            idx[i][1] = heights[i];
        }
        java.util.Arrays.sort(idx, (a, b) -> b[1] - a[1]);
        String[] res = new String[n];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            res[i] = names[idx[i][0]];
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
